# Description

Allows using quotes in bru file to enclose special symbols for bruno keys in the following dictionaries:
fixes #571 
fixes #2878 (alternative)
```
headers {
  "multi word header": value
  "this:header": is illegal HTTP header, but bruno can save it
}

body:form-urlencoded {
  "special:param name": value
}

body:multipart-form {
  "special:file-part name": @file(bruno.json)
  "special:text-part name": value
}

```

